<item>
            <title>[LU-12036] Add &apos;no_create&apos; mount option to create new OSTs inactive</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12036</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When adding new OSTs to an existing filesystem, it&apos;d be nice to have a command line flag to be able to add them to the MGS in an inactive state so that they weren&apos;t used for allocation until the site was ready.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(this should be a non-default flag so it doesn&apos;t break existing behaviour)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
